### ============================================================
### 업적 및 칭호 시스템 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 전체 업적 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 카테고리 코드별 업적 목록 조회
### CategoryCode: MISSION, GUILD, ATTENDANCE, SOCIAL, SPECIAL
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/category/MISSION
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 카테고리별 업적 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/mission-category/1
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 업적 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 완료한 업적 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/my/completed
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 진행 중인 업적 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/my/in-progress
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 수령 가능한 업적 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/my/claimable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 업적 보상 수령
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/1/claim
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 전체 칭호 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 포지션별 칭호 목록 조회
### Position: LEFT, RIGHT
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/position/LEFT
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/position/RIGHT
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 칭호 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 포지션별 칭호 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/my/position/LEFT
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 장착된 칭호 조회 (좌측/우측 모두)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/my/equipped
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 포지션별 장착된 칭호 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/my/equipped/LEFT
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 칭호 장착
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/1/equip
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 특정 포지션 칭호 해제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/unequip/LEFT
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 모든 칭호 해제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/titles/unequip-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 통계 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/stats/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### 랭킹 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 종합 랭킹 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 완료 랭킹 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings/missions?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 연속 활동 랭킹 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings/streaks?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 업적 달성 랭킹 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings/achievements?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 랭킹 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 주변 랭킹 조회 (위아래 N명)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings/nearby?range=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 레벨 랭킹 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings/my/level
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 전체 레벨 랭킹 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings/level?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 카테고리별 레벨 랭킹 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rankings/level/category/HEALTH?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json
